sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Server as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Auth as Authentication<br/>Middleware
    participant IdP as OAuth2 IdP<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Quota as Quota Middleware<br/>(SQLite backing)
    participant ABAC as Access Control<br/>(Cedar ABAC)
    participant Router as Provider Router
    participant vLLM as vLLM Backend<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant VectorDB as Vector DB<br/>(pgvector 5432/TCP)
    participant Safety as Safety Provider
    participant Tool as Tool Runtime<br/>(Brave Search 443/TCP)

    Note over Client,Tool: Flow 1: Inference Request (Chat Completion)
    Client->>Server: POST /v1/inference/chat-completion<br/>Bearer JWT Token
    Server->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth->>IdP: Fetch JWKS keys<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    IdP-->>Auth: JSON Web Key Set
    Auth-->>Server: User attributes extracted
    Server->>Quota: Check rate limit
    Quota-->>Server: Allowed (SQLite KV lookup)
    Server->>ABAC: Check ABAC policy<br/>user × model × action
    ABAC-->>Server: Permitted
    Server->>Router: Route by model ID
    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>API Key Bearer<br/>HTTP/8000
    vLLM-->>Router: Completion response (streaming SSE)
    Router-->>Server: Stream chunks
    Server-->>Client: text/event-stream (SSE)<br/>Configurable TLS

    Note over Client,Tool: Flow 2: RAG Query (Vector I/O)
    Client->>Server: POST /v1/vector-io/query<br/>Bearer JWT Token
    Server->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>Server: Authenticated
    Server->>Quota: Check rate limit
    Quota-->>Server: Allowed
    Server->>Router: Route to embedding provider
    Router->>vLLM: POST /v1/embeddings<br/>API Key Bearer
    vLLM-->>Router: Embedding vectors
    Router->>VectorDB: SQL query (pgvector)<br/>5432/TCP Username/Password<br/>Configurable TLS
    VectorDB-->>Router: Similar document chunks
    Router-->>Server: Query results
    Server-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,Tool: Flow 3: Agent Turn with Tool Use
    Client->>Server: POST /v1/agents/{id}/session/{sid}/turn<br/>Bearer JWT Token
    Server->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>Server: Authenticated
    Server->>Router: Route to agent provider
    Router->>Safety: Input shield check
    Safety-->>Router: Safe
    Router->>vLLM: Chat completion (with tools)<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    vLLM-->>Router: tool_call: brave_search(query)
    Router->>Tool: GET /api/search?q=...<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>API Key
    Tool-->>Router: Search results
    Router->>vLLM: Follow-up completion<br/>(with tool results)
    vLLM-->>Router: Final response
    Router->>Safety: Output shield check
    Safety-->>Router: Safe
    Router-->>Server: Agent turn result
    Server-->>Client: text/event-stream (SSE)
